{"tid":855161,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陳柏宇囡囡取名羿辰","createTime":"2018-10-10T01:21:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T10:49:26.000Z","uid":82917,"like":338,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"5f526ab395bd741ebdfc200b882d714acf039b2e","tid":855161,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T01:21:28.000Z","msg":"歌手陳柏宇（Jason）9月底榮升爸爸後化身「炫娃狂魔」，不時在社交網分享與女兒Abigail的合照，昨日他上載囡囡出世紙，公布為女兒取名「羿辰」。<br />\n<br />\n至於他老婆符曉薇在網上分享餵母乳的點滴：「母乳生活，由呢個BB出世嗰一刻，我嘅母乳生活就開始。原來餵母乳係需要戒口，仲要戒得清過佗B。」她又列了一個很想要的飲食清單，包括薯片、朱古力、麻辣火鍋、麻辣米線、榴槤、珍珠奶茶、和牛、大閘蟹，辣魚蛋，換言之她餵母乳期間，與上述食品無緣。<br />\n<br />\n成個IG都係佢個女 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/10/092051_fab89b53b6876676574aead380608297.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2F092051_fab89b53b6876676574aead380608297.png&h=0fafbdb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個名好有韻味，可以同樂囝個仔余初見上契 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e65036d229f4c8d05e7dac1965631a2206d6ea80","tid":855161,"uid":183383,"like":493,"dislike":2,"score":491,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T01:26:35.000Z","msg":"后羿射日?"},{"pid":"492d07d19c44878e473ad3260d679b407f2b8e71","tid":855161,"uid":82917,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e65036d229f4c8d05e7dac1965631a2206d6ea80","tid":855161,"uid":183383,"like":493,"dislike":2,"score":491,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T01:26:35.000Z","msg":"后羿射日?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T01:28:48.000Z","msg":"屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b34b75eacc4d2a6ac5b0da18fdc780419d75406c","tid":855161,"uid":79442,"like":332,"dislike":2,"score":330,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T01:29:45.000Z","msg":"偽神?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1fbd8fe0b3523acdb4cc27a944980